<topic id='business_definition_specialist_community_public_health_nurse__school_nurse.description'>
  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>NHS Business Definition: Specialist Community Public Health Nurse: School Nurse - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
    <p>
A 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_specialist_community_public_health_nurse__school_nurse">Specialist Community Public Health Nurse: School Nurse</xref>
 is a 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_care_professional">CARE PROFESSIONAL</xref>.        </p>
    <p>
      <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_specialist_community_public_health_nurse__school_nurse">Specialist Community Public Health Nurse - School Nurses</xref>
 provide a variety of services such as:        </p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <div>
          <p>
providing health and sex education within 
                                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_school">Schools</xref>
          </p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <div>
          <p>carrying out developmental screening</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <div>
          <p>undertaking health interviews, administering immunisation programmes etc.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_specialist_community_public_health_nurse__school_nurse">Specialist Community Public Health Nurse - School Nurses</xref>
    <p>
 can be employed either by the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_local_authority">Local Authority</xref>, 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_clinical_commissioning_group">Clinical Commissioning Group</xref>, 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_nhs_trust">NHS Trust</xref>, 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_nhs_foundation_trust">NHS Foundation Trust</xref>
 or by the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_school">School</xref>
 directly.        </p>
  </div>
</body>
